A few things to address so please ensure you communicate this with your members as this will affect all. 

- By Monday afternoon the Spring Season Entry List will be updated & Thursday will be the last time it will be updated for Mixed teams. 
- By Thursday next week the information pack containing numerous information for the season as we have a lot to cover. 

- We are still short referees for next season & if we are unable to get people that can do 3/4 games a night then the only option will be to it back on teams. - We are looking for additional media people that would like to get involved & join the current team, we need 2 for Monday, 4 for Tuesday, 2 for Wednesday. It's only a small role & details will be given to those that come forward.

- Don't forget that we have the special offer for Wednesday Oztag 10's that if you are registered in a team on Monday or Tuesday & sign up for Wednesday Oztag 10's you registration will be $85, not the $110. 

- We will now be offering a similar offer for Wednesday mixed, if you are registered on a team on Monday or Tuesday & register on Wednesday your registration will now be $60, not $90. 

Two amazing offers for you & your members to take advantage of & this will be advertised on Facebook & Instagram on Monday. Don't miss out.
